use this workaround only if you have problems with netbeans

Go to
/home/your_user_name/netbeans-x.x/etc/

see: http://www.mediafire.com/view/?7jlnvd584qlgvcd

PD: 
netbeans-x.x = varies depending on the version, for example:
netbeans-6.5, netbeans-7.1, etc.

rename o backup the file:

netbeans.conf

copy the file netbeans.conf from DkGreen/workaround/Netbeans and paste the file in the folder /home/your_user_name/netbeans-x.x/etc/
